item.dc:creator: @xxlegitxx xxlegitxx
item.description:
@xxlegitxx wrote:

[quote=“exe626, post:7, topic:128855”]Looks kinda like a render dropped onto a bunch of c4ds, and with all honesty it doesn’t look very good.
Theres no flow, the colors are just kinda thrown around, and the render isn’t blended, not one bit.

…

This post honestly makes no since. ‘The render needs something doing to it’ - ‘Maybe blend the background a little’. That makes no since, and I’m pretty sure I’m not the only one confused by it.

Edits made:
Brush strokes, photofliters(x3), Gradient map(x2), Gaussian blur.
[IMG ]http://i195.photobucket.com/albums/z20/Exe626/lawl-1.png[/img ]

I only did this so you can get an idea to what you can do to it, a few simple steps and you can change that into this.[/quote]

Border and it would look perfect.
